# Unit Tests

Place unit tests in this directory.

Unit tests should:
- Test individual functions/classes in isolation
- Mock all external dependencies
- Be fast (<100ms per test)
- Cover edge cases and error conditions

Example structure:
```
unit/
├── services/
│   ├── passwordSecurity.test.ts
│   └── sessionManager.test.ts
├── middleware/
│   ├── jwtAuth.test.ts
│   └── validation.test.ts
└── utils/
    └── helpers.test.ts
```
